Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========正文==========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开玲子的遗物干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉  一如既往地让人搞不懂的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜籽  嘴两边  两粒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  不知不觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次还给妖怪名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子的记忆成为思念  注入我的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子这个人  一点点地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向图书馆借的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是忘记还了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车票？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得是哪方错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙说油炸豆腐清汤面里的豆腐是先吃的  难以置信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是先吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐是要浸在汤汁里最后吃的  是吧夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  豆腐是要趁甜味没有被汤汁冲淡前吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…我是觉得怎么都可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐要后吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐要先吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这么争论之前  那个不叫豆腐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是后吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  正和我意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  你掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是过去的车票吧  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟夏目有什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么说道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样…今早上学时捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拙劣的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会再好好问你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃也没用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里…回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去那张车票的站头吧  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才没看清楚  忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}笹{\r}田  你为什么这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  自上次的试胆大会以来  我真的想见个面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见谁  你真讨厌  这不明摆着的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧  车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你掉东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没掉东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  到底我掉了什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算来了吗  真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里已经不使用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像很久之前就成为废线了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凄凉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾沼是在另一边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为什么玲子又…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么热还真亏它能睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玲子  终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  别搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是玲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我不是玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  想点办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在说什么都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么坏东西  你就陪他玩一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  玲子死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是孙子嘛  气味相似也不足为奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用闻得这么细致入微
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  浓毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说在这里等玲子  是不是有什么约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她说会和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾沼  玲子要和你一起去雾沼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雾沼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗡嗡地叫  说「不会原谅你的」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是玲子就说「不行啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这家伙来说明还真是为难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许这家伙在友人帐上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把名字还给它的话  思念会传达给我们事由的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字  我叫三都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之守护哟  昭显其名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气的是实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢那个叫实栗的妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢实栗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:09:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是实栗说讨厌我  不想再见我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做错什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那实栗对你说了什么生气的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像多少有点明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗生气的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊  玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾沼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾沼  邻站的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  那我和你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今天天色已晚  明天再在此碰头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  没能完成约定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是玲子有了什么不能来的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方可能已经不在等待了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去一下是不会知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去  要完成玲子没做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今天天色已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天放学后我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  还是现在就动身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  轻易就答应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾沼附近可没有公交车通过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道走过去要多久吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那肯定天都黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是白说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子不来的话  你一个人不也可以去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就这么傻等着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为约好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻  居然去问他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始变冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像山间的寒风在流入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说这家伙是可爱呢还是烦人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到实栗的话  准备怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  没想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和好的话  得说点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别让他们见面比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许反而会变麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都  在到达之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想好要说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:12:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨念？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会原谅  不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓稳咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是三都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来实栗被地灵附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被地灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为地灵喜好愤怒及仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗对三都如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要去见对方为好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得怎样我都不管了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啊  猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊  仿佛不是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是山间的寒风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怨念所致吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗  出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗  有话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都  实栗长什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…小小的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的  是多小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么小吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是开玩笑的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么在  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲇…鲇鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那就是实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分明是奇大无比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办夏目  要说服它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子  是夏目玲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好  把友人帐交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐在那里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是玲子的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:17:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗  实栗  是我  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好  快醒过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗  快回来  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帐给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很可怜  看来跟地灵一起消失在沼泽底了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  到底搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  三都你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要干什么笨蛋  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  很恶心啊  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说放开我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  吵架是因为玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因为夏目玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这蠢货把重要的名字给了玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有作为妖怪的自尊吗  你这大蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来再也不想见你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又恬不知耻地出现了  你这呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:18:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不用这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都喜欢你  所以一直牵挂着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说它蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心道歉的话给我快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直心不在焉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  实栗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  看仔细了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有在听吗浓毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个家伙  早就和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实栗  我们回山里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说也会回去的  你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  真的谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  别向人类低头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  他把名字也还给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说别低头了  你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  又不知不觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把它放回原处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说玲子没能完成约定是因为有特别的原因对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太瞧得起她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一不小心忘记了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子就是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么随便…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这书是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是借着没还吗  瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看来忘了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去真像是有特别原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  玲子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:21:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那算是什么啊  真莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为是好朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  昨天怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下  这个拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}笹{\r}田  {\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}笹{\r}田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天妇罗面条里的虾  你是先吃还是后吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好朋友…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天  谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你很为难嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉入了水坝的村子出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栖身在那的妖怪们为了要回名字而来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.24,0:23:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你这家伙  别缠住夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时要麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.91,0:23:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见的人…
